## Controlling the Drawer

You can open/close the drawer programmatically using `navigation` methods:

```jsx
// Inside a screen
navigation.openDrawer();
navigation.closeDrawer();
navigation.toggleDrawer();
```

You can also add a header button to open the drawer, e.g., a hamburger icon.
